Code coverage
=============

In order to have code coverage active, you need to install PHP_CodeCoverage:
https://github.com/sebastianbergmann/php-code-coverage

You will also need php-pecl-xdebug and php-pecl-json RPM packages to be installed.

Mock functions
==============

Install 'runkit' pecl extension first:
pecl install channel://pecl.php.net/runkit-0.9

and add /etc/php.d/runkit.ini:
extension=runkit.so
